This paper is about a collection of text documents for automatic document classification in Czech language. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with natural language processing and computational linguistics. The paper also mentions the evaluation of multi-label document classification approaches, which falls under the sub-category cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Additionally, the paper discusses the results of state-of-the-art methods, which could be related to sub-categories such as cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.CY (Computers and Society).
